   <text type="edition">
      <body>
         
         <pb n="#f38v"/>
         
         <milestone unit="notice" xml:id="notice_éléphant"/>
         <div type="title">
            <head>
               <lb facs="#z1" style="title" rend="red"/>De elephante &per; qu&em; quilibet fidelis
            </head>
         </div>
         
         <div type="ethology">
            <p>
               <lb facs="#z2"/>Est a&nim;al &qui; &dicitur; <persName ref="#éléphant">elephans</persName>, elafio grece mons
               
               <lb facs="#z3"/>&dicitur; latine, et ideo &dicitur; uocatum a magnitudine cor- 
               
               <lb facs="#z4"/>poris. Dentes ei&us; sunt ebur. Lucas uocat <persName ref="#éléphant">&eum;</persName> bou&em; quia 
               
               <lb facs="#z5"/>null&um; a&nim;al uidet&ur; &esse; mai&us; eo. Et ideo &per;git
               p&zz;&us; ad &pmacron;li-
               
               <lb facs="#z6"/>um : quia aptum &eius; &pmacron;lio et
               pon&unt; su&per; <persName ref="#éléphant">e&um;</persName> turr&em; de&qua; dimicant &quasi; de quod&am; castel- 
               
               <lb facs="#z7"/>lo. Si <persName ref="#éléphants">plures</persName> sunt : gregatim incedunt motu quo ualent saltant auersi
               coe&unt;. 
               
               <lb facs="#z8"/>&Non; ampli&usf; &qua;m semel gignunt. Pri&us; fuerunt
               &apud; <placeName ref="#Afrique">a<choice>
                  <orig>ff</orig>
                  <reg>f</reg>
               </choice>ricam</placeName> et <placeName ref="#Inde">indiam</placeName> : &sed; modo 
               
               <lb facs="#z9"/>sunt in|sola <placeName ref="#Afrique">a<choice>
                  <orig>ff</orig>
                  <reg>f</reg>
               </choice>rica</placeName>. Truncos comedunt : et arenam bibunt. Dormientes n&um;&qua;m
               
               <lb
                  facs="#z10"/>rec&um;bant &sed; &quando; lassi sunt applicant se qui&bus;dam
               arbori&bus; et ita fulti dormiunt. 
               
               <lb facs="#z11"/>Cum autem aliquis uult eas
               ca&per;e : succidit arbores pene totas ante&qua;m applic&ant; 
               
               <lb facs="#z12"/>se ibi
               et &primus; conueni&unt; applicat&ur;i : cadunt cum &ipsius; arbori&bus; et quia
               &non; &habent; 
               
               <lb facs="#z13"/>iuncturas unde possunt surgere : gem&unt; deni&que;
               garriunt. &Quod; si solus est : ue- 
               
               <lb facs="#z14"/>nit <persName ref="#éléphants">alter</persName> qui releuare <persName ref="#éléphant">eum</persName> cupit
               &#38; quia &non; potest : plorant nimis garrit. 
               
               <lb facs="#z15"/>Tunc <persName ref="#éléphants">multi alii</persName>
               ueniunt et c&um; &non; queunt adiuvare &eum; : &omnes; simul garriunt. 
               
               <lb facs="#z16"/>Deni&que; audita tanta uoce : currit uenator et occidit <persName ref="#éléphant">eum</persName>. &Sed;
               &tantum; sepe e&uenit; 
               
               <lb facs="#z17"/>&quando; &omnes; ita garriunt : &quidam;
               un&us; <persName ref="#paruulus">&par;uulus</persName> ea&rum2; venit ibi et ponit os su&um; &pro;muscid&em; 
               
               <lb facs="#z18"/>subt&us; magn&um; ill&um; <persName ref="#éléphant">elephant&em;</persName> et sic eleuat eum os sic
               euadit ab insidiatore. 
               
               <lb facs="#z19"/>&Habent; &autem; hoc &pro;&zz;p&um; &qui; ubi
               fuerit os et peliis &huius; <persName ref="#paruulus">&par;uulus elephantis</persName> incensa : fum&us; ero&rum; 
               
               <lb facs="#z20"/>fugat serpentes et &omnem; uenen&um;, uel siqua fuer&unt; noxia.
               Sciend&um; enim &qui; h<choice>
                  <orig>u</orig>
                  <reg>uius</reg>
               </choice> ele- 
               
               <lb facs="#z21"/>phantes null&am; &habent; concupiscenti&am; carnis.
               &Sed; c&um; uolunt filios &pro;creare : uad&unt; 
               
               <lb facs="#z22"/>uter&que; <persName ref="#éléphant">masculus</persName>
               et <persName ref="#éléphante">fe&mina;</persName> ad orient&em; us&que; ad <placeName ref="#paradis">&para;dysum</placeName>. Est &autem2; ibi <persName ref="#mandragore">herba</persName> 
               
               <lb facs="#z23"/>&quae; &dicitur; <persName ref="#mandragore">mandragora</persName>, &qui; comedit <persName ref="#éléphante">fe&mina;</persName> et &primus;
               seducit <persName ref="#éléphant">mascul&um;</persName> ut manducet, 
               
               <lb facs="#z24"/>deni&que; conueni&unt; simul, et
               statim <persName ref="#éléphante">femina</persName> concipit. C&um; &autem; t&em;p&us; pariendi ue- 
               
               <lb facs="#z25"/>nit
               uadit in <placeName ref="#Eau">a&qua;m</placeName> us&que; ad ubera et ibi parit &pro;pter <persName ref="#dragon">dracon&em;</persName> qu&em; &habent;
               insidia- 
               
               <pb n="#f39r"/>              
               <fw place="top-right" type="foliono">39</fw>
               
               <lb facs="#z26"/>torem. Et hoc facit semel post centum annos ideo parit in <placeName ref="#Eau">a&qua;</placeName> ne
               cadat <persName ref="#éléphanteau">pusillus</persName> ad 
               
               <lb facs="#z27"/>terram quia &non; posset surgere iuncturis carens
               et ne <persName ref="#dragon">draco</persName> devoret <persName ref="#éléphanteau">pusill&um;</persName> &eius;. Inte- 
               
               <lb facs="#z28"/>rim <persName ref="#éléphant">masculus</persName> custodit
               ill&am; parient&em; &pro;pter <persName ref="#dragon">dracon&em;</persName> que uult eripere <persName ref="#éléphanteau">pusill&um;</persName> &eius; et con-
               
               <lb facs="#z29"/>culcare us&que; ad mort&em;.</p>
         </div>
         
         <div type="symbolism">
            
            <p> &Non; possunt &omnia; h<choice>
               <orig>e</orig>
               <reg>ae</reg>
            </choice>c accipi ad significa&tionem; &sed; ad &uer;itatem 
               
               <lb/><seg facs="#z30"
               >rei. Duo elephantes figurant <persName ref="#Adam">ad&am;</persName> et <persName ref="#Eve">ev&am;</persName> qui erant </seg>
               <seg facs="#z31">&in; <placeName ref="#paradis">paradiso</placeName> sine concupiscentia</seg>
               
               <lb/><seg facs="#z32">carnali et figur&ant; <add place="above">eti&am;</add>
                  qu&em;libet fidel&em;. De isto </seg>
               <seg facs="#z33">&dicitur; &quia; &per;git &pri;m&us; ad &pmacron;li&um; ita et
                  bonus</seg>
               
               <lb/><seg facs="#z34"><persName ref="#Humanité">&homo;</persName> &pri;m&us; stat in acie sp&um;ali et &pri;m&us;
                  accusator &esse; sui.</seg>
               <seg facs="#z35">Su&per; <add place="above">ilium</add> pon&itur; turris : unde alii
                  se</seg>
               
               <lb/><seg facs="#z36">defendant, de bono ist&ius; exemplo &non; solum </seg>
               
               <seg facs="#z37">&pro;tegunt&ur; alii &sed; et &ipse; defendit eos &oratio;-</seg>
               
               <lb/><seg facs="#z38">nib&us; suis. Si plures &sunt; gregatim incedunt</seg>
               
               <seg facs="#z39"> &quia; sem&per; &sunt; concordantes ad &in;vicem</seg>
               
               <lb/><seg facs="#z40">boni. Illi motu quo ualent saltant simil&itur; </seg>
               
               <seg facs="#z41">et isti nitant&ur; de &uer;tute &in; &uer;tutem.</seg>
               
               <lb/><seg facs="#z42">Illi &autem2; si coeunt et &non; amplius &qua;m semel gi <choice>
                  <orig>n</orig>
                  <reg/>
               </choice>gn&unt;,</seg>
               
               <seg facs="#z43"> ita et istis est contrari&um;</seg>
               
               <lb/><seg facs="#z44">gignere et omnis delectatio carnis </seg>
               
               <seg facs="#z45">et &omnio; cauent &habere; &nisi; unam uxor&em;. Truncos</seg>
               
               <lb/><seg facs="#z46">comedunt illi et haren&am; bib&unt; </seg>
               
               <seg facs="#z47">et isti illos qui &sunt; &quasi; trunci de decorati et
                  &in;com-</seg>
               
               <lb/><seg facs="#z48">positi morib&us; et alios quos deducit </seg>
               
               <seg facs="#z49">mundus &quasi; harena huc et illuc traiciunt</seg>
               
               <lb/><seg facs="#z50">insem<choice>
                  <orig>e</orig>
                  <reg>ina</reg>
               </choice>ti &pmacron;it et faciunt de illis fr&em;s </seg>
               
               <seg facs="#z51">et <persName ref="#Humanité">filios suos</persName>, et eti&am; reme<choice>
                  <orig>n</orig>
                  <reg>m</reg>
               </choice>bra sua. &Unde; &dicitur;</seg>
               
               <lb/><seg facs="#z52">petro de disco illo macta et manduca. </seg>
               
               <seg facs="#z53">Dormientes n&um;&quam; rec&um;b&ant; et &contra; ut su&pra;.</seg>
               
               <lb/><seg facs="#z54">Si<add place="above">c</add> religiosi uiri num&quam; us&que; </seg>
               
               <seg facs="#z55">ad satietat&em; dormiunt, </seg>
               
               <seg facs="#z56">&sed; stando &pmacron;gustant. Et &quia;</seg>
               
               <lb/><seg facs="#z57">inclinant se quib&us;d&am; arborib&us; </seg>
               
               <seg facs="#z58">cadunt cum &ipsius;. </seg>
               
               <seg facs="#z59"> Per arbores &huius; intelligit&ur;</seg>
               
               <lb/><seg facs="#z60">terrena substantia, cum qui se </seg>
               
               <seg facs="#z61">inclinat cadit cum </seg>
               
               <seg facs="#z62">&ipsa;, et ideo cecidit &pri;m&us;</seg>
               
               <lb/><seg facs="#z63"><persName ref="#Adam">&homo;</persName> et <persName ref="#Humanité">&omnis; &pro;genies</persName> eius, quia </seg>
               
               <seg facs="#z64">plus inclinauit se arbori </seg>
               
               <seg facs="#z65">&quam; debuit. &Qui; <choice>
                  <orig>&pri;</orig>
                  <reg>per</reg>
               </choice>&qua;m</seg>
               
               <lb/><seg facs="#z66">cecidit &non; potuit surgere </seg>
               
               <seg facs="#z67">per se &quia; de illo &dicitur;.</seg>
               
               <seg facs="#z68">Nichil potestis sine me fa&cie;</seg>
               
               <lb/><seg facs="#z69">et &quia; &non; potuit surgere </seg> iacens clamauit ad
               cui&us; 
              
              <seg facs="#z70">uoc&em; uenerunt <persName ref="#éléphants">alli</persName> et cla-</seg>
               
               <lb/><seg facs="#z71">mauerunt c&um; eo, &sed; &non; potue&runt;</seg>
               
               <seg facs="#z72"> adiuuare <persName ref="#éléphant">eum</persName>. &Quod2;</seg>
               
               <seg facs="#z73"> c&um; audiuit uenator &uenit;</seg>
               
               <lb/><seg facs="#z74">et occidit e&um;. Isti qui</seg>
               
               <seg facs="#z75"> uolue&rint; adiuuare: sunt <persName ref="#prophetes">&pro;&phete;</persName></seg>
               
               <seg facs="#z76"> et &patri;arche &sed; &non; potue-</seg>
               
               <lb/><seg facs="#z77">runt, ideo uulnerauit eos <add place="above">eum</add></seg>
               
               <seg facs="#z78"> <persName ref="#diable">diabolus</persName> us&que; mort&em;</seg>
               
               <seg facs="#z79"> sicut &scrip;t&um; &est; de illo.</seg>
               
               <lb/><seg facs="#z80"><quote source="Luc 10, 30">qui descendebat ab ier<choice>
                  <orig>l&#859;</orig>
                  <reg>usale</reg>
               </choice>m in ierico.</quote></seg>
               
               <seg facs="#z81"> Simili<choice>
                  <orig>t&#859;</orig>
                  <reg>tudines</reg>
               </choice> et alii qui se c&om;mitt&unt; terre-</seg>
               
               <lb/><seg facs="#z82">ne substanti<choice>
                  <orig>e</orig>
                  <reg>ae</reg>
               </choice> et deferent <persName ref="#Dieu">de&um;</persName> et &per;eunt</seg>
               
               <seg facs="#z83">et &tantum; ali&quam; uenit <persName ref="#paruulus">&par;uulus</persName></seg>
               
               <lb/><seg facs="#z84">et adiuuat eum. <persName ref="#paruulus">Paruulus</persName></seg>
               
               <seg facs="#z85">iste &est; <persName ref="#JC">&dominus; &noster;</persName>. &Unde; &dicitur;.</seg>
               
               <seg facs="#z86">Et aduoc&ant; <persName ref="#JC">&iheso;</persName> <persName ref="#paruulus">&par;uul&um;</persName></seg>
               
               <lb/><seg facs="#z87">et &cum;. <persName ref="#paruulus">Paruulus</persName> est &homo; &quia; fact&us;</seg>
               
               <seg facs="#z88"><damage agent="hole"/></seg>
               
               <seg facs="#z89">&est;. &Quod2; eleuauit iacentem : quasi mortu&us;</seg>
               
               <lb/><seg facs="#z90">&est; &propter; peccatores et liberauit a potestate</seg>
               
               <seg facs="#z91"><persName ref="#diable">diaboli</persName>. Cui&us; os et pellis et &cum;.</seg>
               
               <pb n="#f39v"/>
               
               <lb facs="#z92"/>Per os &qui; est fortitudo corporis: intellig&itur; deitas et per
               pellem humanitas 
               
               <lb facs="#z93"/>id est ubicumque habitat <persName ref="#JC">&christus;</persName> qui &est;
               <persName ref="#Dieu">&deus;</persName> et &homo;, fugiunt &omnia; uenena et &omnis; 
               
               <lb facs="#z94"/>potestates
               inimici. Sequ&itur;. Elephantes &non; &habent; null&am; concupiscenti&am; carnis 
               
               <lb
                  facs="#z95"/>et &cetera;. Isti &significant; <persName ref="#Adam">ad&am;</persName> et <persName ref="#Eve">ev&am;</persName> qui &non; habebant
               concupiscenti&am; &antequam; 
               
               <lb facs="#z96"/>coe&unt; &in; obedientes et &tamen;
               nudi erant. Cum &autem2; c&om;mederunt de <persName ref="#fruit_défendu">fructu</persName> 
               
               <lb facs="#z97"/>in obedientie per
               seduction&em; <persName ref="#diable">diaboli</persName> ; concepit <persName ref="#Eve">mulier</persName> extra <placeName ref="#paradis">paradis&um;</placeName>. 
               
               <lb facs="#z98"/>Post&qua;m expuli sunt de <placeName ref="#paradis">&para;dyso</placeName> ; uenit &in; hunc mund&um; uelut &in; magn&am;
               
               <lb facs="#z99"/><placeName ref="#Eau">aqu&am;</placeName>, ubi <persName ref="#éléphante">fe&mina;</persName> &par;turit &pro;lem su&am; &pro;pter
               <persName ref="#dragon">dracon&em;</persName>. Hic sign&um; <placeName ref="#Eau">a&qua;</placeName> : hunc 
               
               <lb facs="#z100"/>mund&um;, &propter;
               tempestates. &Unde; &dicitur; salu&um; me fac <persName ref="#Dieu">&deus;</persName> &quoniam; <quote
                  source="Ps 69(68), 2"><choice>
                     <orig>i</orig>
                     <reg>intraverunt</reg>
                  </choice>
                  <choice>
                     <orig>a</orig>
                     <reg>aquae</reg>
                  </choice>
                  <choice>
                     <orig>u</orig>
                     <reg>usque</reg>
                  </choice>
                  <choice>
                     <orig>a</orig>
                     <reg>ad</reg>
                  </choice>
                  <choice>
                     <orig>a</orig>
                     <reg>animam</reg>
                  </choice>
                  <choice>
                     <orig>m</orig>
                     <reg>meam</reg>
                  </choice></quote>
               
               <lb facs="#z101"/>Que tu&um; debet parere : intrat &in; <placeName ref="#Eau">a&qua;m</placeName> us&que; ad ubera. In
               uberib&us; &est; mag- 
               
               <lb facs="#z102"/>na luxuria et ideo intrat ibi usque &in;
               <placeName ref="#Eau">a&qua;m</placeName> quia c&um; c&om;pleuerit luxuri&am; 
               
               <lb facs="#z103"/>suam, concipit
               dolor&em; et post pe&per;it iniquitat&em;. Et hoc facit &in; <placeName ref="#Eau">aqu&am;</placeName> ne 
               
               <lb
                  facs="#z104"/>cadit ad terr&am;, id est ne ex toto cadat in terrenis &quia;
               mollior est sub- 
               
               <lb facs="#z105"/>stantia aque <placeName ref="#Eau">&qua;m </placeName>terre, id est min&us; &enim;
               cadere &in; <placeName ref="#Eau">a&qua;</placeName> &quasi; ad terr&am;. Quia 
               
               <lb facs="#z106"/>si &omnio; ad heserit
               terrenis : <persName ref="#dragon">draco</persName> &idest; <persName ref="#diable">diabolus</persName> devorabit e&um;. masculus 
               
               <lb facs="#z107"/>e&am;
               <supplied reason="illegible">custodit</supplied> d&um; parit quia <persName ref="#JC">&dominus;
               &noster;</persName> qui uir est et &capellae; &uestrum; sem&per; custo- 
               
               <lb facs="#z108"/>dit
               <supplied reason="illegible">suus</supplied> et &in; terra et &in; <placeName ref="#Eau">aqua</placeName>. Hoc semel
               facium post &cent; annos <add facs="#z110" place="margin right">Simili<choice>
                  <orig>t&#859;</orig>
                  <reg>tudines</reg>
               </choice> et boni que non curant nisi de primis nuptus et hoc post centum <choice>
                  <orig>ā</orig>
                  <reg>an</reg>
               </choice>no</add> id est 
               
               <lb facs="#z109"/>c&um; ad &per;fectam etat&em;
               ueni&unt;, &non; preueni&unt; t&em;p&us; : sicut stulti faciunt.</p>
